ory with 28 medals,said the World Anti-Doping Agency, which conducted the 2021 tests, can no longer be trusted.\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2030, \"end\": 2036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999884039, \"rank\": 1.1675100033357301e-11, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The body\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"its fairness\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"the most decorated athlete\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"28 medals\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Anti-Doping Agency\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2132}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2021 tests\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was also targeted by a US federal investigation for accepting the explanation for 2021 test results when travel to China was not possible due to the Covid pandemic.\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2219, \"end\": 2221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.752206237571385, \"rank\": 0.324666234002165, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2311, \"end\": 2316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9991943974789522, \"rank\": 0.0008055427288771855, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour